  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>The Office Cleaner is accountable for maintaining a clean and organized workspace in an office setting and is expected to perform various cleaning tasks efficiently and diligently, following established protocols and safety guidelines.</p><p>Working days: Mon - Fri (not inclusive cleaning a toilet)<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities::</strong></p><ol><li>Pantry Management</li><li>Cleaning and Sanitizing</li><li>Trash Management:</li><li>Restocking Supplies:</li><li>Adherence to Company Policies:</li></ol><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience as a cleaner or janitor in an office or similar environment is advantageous</li><li>Knowledge of proper cleaning techniques</li><li>Attention to detail and the ability to maintain high cleanliness standards.</li><li>Reliability and punctuality in attending to assigned cleaning duties.</li><li>Full Time 5 days per week</li></ul>",
